      <Value><![CDATA[<p>Queen Margaret University (QMU) is a Data Controller in terms of the Data Protection Act 2018 (DPA) and the UK General Data Protection Regulations. The University is registered with the <strong>Information Commissioner’s Office</strong>. Our Registration Number is Z6013920.</p>]]></Value>
    </bodyTop>
    <centralBlocks>
      <Value><![CDATA[[
  {
    "key": "20f8371f-e0c0-4a4f-b979-55335e9e60a1",
    "name": "The type of personal data we collect",
    "ncContentTypeAlias": "centralBlocks",
    "title": "The type of personal data we collect",
    "content": "<p>We collect and process the following types of personal data: </p>\n<p><span class=\"lead\">Events and Conferences</span></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Name</li>\n<li>Job title and organisation</li>\n<li>Email address</li>\n<li>Postal address (where applicable)</li>\n<li>Telephone number</li>\n<li>Dietary requirement</li>\n<li>Accessibility requirements</li>\n<li>Payment details</li>\n<li>Vehicle registration</li>\n</ul>\n<p><span class=\"lead\">Summer accommodation</span></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Name</li>\n<li>Job title and organisation</li>\n<li>Email address</li>\n<li>Postal address (where applicable)</li>\n<li>Telephone number</li>\n<li>Dietary requirement</li>\n<li>Accessibility requirements</li>\n<li>Payment details</li>\n<li>Vehicle registration</li>\n<li>Name of Fringe show associated with booking (if August booking)</li>\n<li>Venue of Fringe show associated with booking (if August booking)</li>\n</ul>\n<p><span class=\"lead\">Sport and Fitness</span></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Name</li>\n<li>Contact details including telephone number, postal address and email address</li>\n<li>Emergency contact details</li>\n<li>Date of birth</li>\n<li>Relevant information about health conditions and medications</li>\n<li>Payment details</li>\n<li>Vehicle registration</li>\n</ul>\n<p><span class=\"lead\">Catering</span> <br />Catering is provided by a third party, BaxterStorey.</p>"
  },
  {
    "key": "53a2bd86-dc09-449e-b831-894bba6e6c03",
    "name": "How we collect your personal data",
    "ncContentTypeAlias": "centralBlocks",
    "title": "How we collect your personal data",
    "content": "<p>We collect your personal data directly from you in relation to all our commercial services. Occasionally the event organiser will collect your personal data and share it with us where that is necessary for the purposes of organising and hosting the event.</p>"
  },
  {
    "key": "e0af967e-6e15-41ee-8d9e-da56f7b0b385",
    "name": "Why we collect your personal data",
    "ncContentTypeAlias": "centralBlocks",
    "title": "Why we collect your personal data",
    "content": "<p>The purpose and basis for processing your personal data is as follows:</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span class=\"lead\">Events and Conferences</span></p>\n<table border=\"1\" style=\"border-collapse: collapse; width: 100%;\">\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th style=\"width: 50%;\">Legal Basis</th>\n<th style=\"width: 50%;\">Purpose</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 50%;\">Consent</td>\n<td style=\"width: 50%;\">\n<ul>\n<li>To process your enquiry</li>\n<li>To keep you up to date on any offers and for marketing purposes</li>\n<li>To provide you with a parking space</li>\n</ul>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 50%;\">Performance of a contract</td>\n<td style=\"width: 50%;\">\n<ul>\n<li>To process your booking</li>\n<li>Provide details on an event</li>\n</ul>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 50%;\">Legitimate interest</td>\n<td style=\"width: 50%;\">\n<ul>\n<li>To gather post-event feedback</li>\n<li>CCTV in place for security purposes</li>\n</ul>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span class=\"lead\">Eventbrite</span></p>\n<p>We use Eventbrite for registration at some of our events. Please note that Eventbrite is a third-party service that is not owned or managed by Queen Margaret University. You should refer to Eventbrite’s terms and conditions of privacy policy. For further details, please see:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Eventbrite terms and conditions</li>\n<li>Eventbrite privacy policy</li>\n</ol>\n<p> </p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span class=\"lead\">Sport and Fitness</span></p>\n<table border=\"1\" style=\"border-collapse: collapse; width: 100%; height: 664px;\">\n<thead>\n<tr style=\"height: 18px;\">\n<th style=\"width: 50%; height: 18px;\">Legal Basis</th>\n<th style=\"width: 50%; height: 18px;\">Purpose</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr style=\"height: 228px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 50%; height: 228px;\">Consent</td>\n<td style=\"width: 50%; height: 228px;\">\n<ul>\n<li>To process your enquiry</li>\n<li>To send updates to members about the Centre’s activities that members can get involved in or any other relevant news about the Centre</li>\n<li>To market the Centre to former members or prospective members where we have consent to do so</li>\n<li>To provide you with a parking permit (public members only)</li>\n<li>To provide members with the best services in line with their current health status</li>\n</ul>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 209px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 50%; height: 209px;\">Performance of a contract</td>\n<td style=\"width: 50%; height: 209px;\">\n<ul>\n<li>To process your booking</li>\n<li>To provide you with a membership to our facilities</li>\n<li>To ensure you are provided with a service which meets your individual needs</li>\n<li>To provide access to the facilities and services offered by the Centre</li>\n<li>To process financial transactions to ensure the efficient and timely management of payment to use our facilities</li>\n</ul>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 173px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 50%; height: 173px;\">Legitimate interest</td>\n<td style=\"width: 50%; height: 173px;\">\n<ul>\n<li>To gather feedback CCTV in place for security purposes</li>\n<li>To have an emergency contact in place for the safety and security of our members</li>\n<li>For legal and regulatory purposes (for example child protection and health and safety) and to comply with its legal obligations and duties of care.</li>\n</ul>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 18px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 50%; height: 18px;\">Legal Obligation</td>\n<td style=\"width: 50%; height: 18px;\">\n<ul>\n<li>For legal and regulatory purposes (for example child protection and health and safety) and to comply with its legal obligations and duties of care.</li>\n</ul>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p> </p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span class=\"lead\">Summer Accommodation</span></p>\n<table border=\"1\" style=\"border-collapse: collapse; width: 100%;\">\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th style=\"width: 50%;\">Legal Basis</th>\n<th style=\"width: 50%;\">Purpose</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 50%;\">Consent</td>\n<td style=\"width: 50%;\">\n<ul>\n<li>To process your enquiry</li>\n<li>To keep you up to date on any offers and for marketing purposes</li>\n<li>To provide you with a parking space</li>\n<li>To inform you of events taking place at the time of your booking</li>\n</ul>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 50%;\">Performance of a contract</td>\n<td style=\"width: 50%;\">\n<ul>\n<li>To process your booking</li>\n<li>Provide details on your booking</li>\n</ul>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 50%;\">Legitimate interest</td>\n<td style=\"width: 50%;\">\n<ul>\n<li>To gather feedback</li>\n<li>CCTV in place for security purposes</li>\n</ul>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span class=\"lead\">Special Categories of Personal Information</span></p>\n<p>We sometimes process special category personal data. Where we process special category data or criminal conviction data we are required to identify an additional legal basis for processing. Special category data is held in the strictest confidence and only shared on a strict need to know basis.</p>\n<p> </p>\n<table border=\"1\" style=\"border-collapse: collapse; width: 100%;\">\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th style=\"width: 50%;\">Additional Legal Basis</th>\n<th style=\"width: 50%;\">Type of Data and Purpose</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 50%;\">Explicit consent</td>\n<td style=\"width: 50%;\">\n<ul>\n<li>Health information to provide any assistance or reasonable adjustments when accessing our events.</li>\n<li>Health information to provide members with the best services in line with their current health. This information may also be used to provide or seek appropriate medical care, and to take appropriate action in the event of an emergency, incident or accident, including by disclosing details of an individual’s health to medical professionals where it is in the individual’s interests to do so</li>\n</ul>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>"
  },
  {
    "key": "6d801740-fde2-467b-a2d9-a8082f338667",
    "name": "How we store your personal data",
    "ncContentTypeAlias": "centralBlocks",
    "title": "How we store your personal data",
    "content": "<p>The University will manage your information securely and will restrict access to only those who need to use it in the course of their duties. The University will put in place technical and organisational measures necessary to ensure the security of your information.</p>\n<p>We will only retain your information as long as is reasonably necessary for the purpose it was gathered and in accordance with QMU’s Retention Schedule. We may be required to keep some of your personal information permanently for historical and archival purposes.</p>"
  },
  {
    "key": "d1d5563c-3b41-4049-8365-b5c309e39db8",
    "name": "Sharing your personal data",
    "ncContentTypeAlias": "centralBlocks",
    "title": "Sharing your personal data",
    "content": "<p>The University will only disclose your information to third parties where we:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Have a legal basis to do so under the UK General Data Protection Regulation; or</li>\n<li>Are required to under a statutory or regulatory obligation; or</li>\n<li>Have your consent.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Reasons we may share your personal data:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>With third party suppliers to meet dietary requirements</li>\n<li>For August Summer Accommodation bookings we partner with the Fringe. We may share your contact details used at the time of the booking with the Fringe so they can contact you about events on campus at the time of your booking. </li>\n</ul>"
  },
  {
    "key": "54bb9ea5-b38c-4ca6-9120-c147c513afb3",
    "name": "Profiling or automated decision making",
    "ncContentTypeAlias": "centralBlocks",
    "title": "Profiling or automated decision making",
    "content": "<p>We do not use profiling or automated decision-making processes. Some processes are semi-automated but a human decision maker will always be involved before any decision is reached in relation to you.</p>"
  },
  {
    "key": "9e96e6f4-8c80-4c58-9cf4-9e4b7ab5469e",
    "name": "Use of our Website",
    "ncContentTypeAlias": "centralBlocks",
    "title": "Use of our Website",
    "content": "<p>QMU respects the privacy of every individual who visits our websites or responds to our interactive advertisements. The <a href=\"/{localLink:umb://document/73b2d17b7aa04fd390efb3de3471a9de}\" title=\"Terms of Use\">Privacy Statement</a> on our website outlines the information we collect via its various web pages and how we use that information. The Statement also instructs you on what to do if you do not want your personal information collected or shared when you visit QMU's website or respond to our advertisements.</p>"
  },
  {
    "key": "c72c5792-e5cd-4ac4-abde-9db49082c488",
    "name": "Your rights relating to your personal information",
    "ncContentTypeAlias": "centralBlocks",
    "title": "Your rights relating to your personal information",
    "content": "<p>Under data protection law, you have rights including:</p>\n<p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Your right of access</span> - You have the right to ask us for copies of your personal information.</p>\n<p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Your right to rectification</span> - You have the right to ask us to rectify personal information you think is inaccurate. You also have the right to ask us to complete information you think is incomplete.</p>\n<p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Your right to erasure</span> - You have the right to ask us to erase your personal information in certain circumstances.</p>\n<p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Your right to restriction of processing</span> - You have the right to ask us to restrict the processing of your personal information in certain circumstances.</p>\n<p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Your right to object to processing</span> - You have the right to object to the processing of your personal information in certain circumstances.</p>\n<p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Your right to data portability</span> - You have the right to ask that we transfer the personal information you gave us to another organisation, or to you, in certain circumstances.</p>\n<p>You are not required to pay any charge for exercising your rights. If you make a request, we have one month to respond to you.</p>\n<p>If you wish to make a rights request the relevant contact details can be found at the end of this statement.</p>"
  },
  {
    "key": "238a854a-e2c0-4ac1-be49-f9d2a046060b",
    "name": "Changes to our privacy statement",
    "ncContentTypeAlias": "centralBlocks",
    "title": "Changes to our privacy statement",
    "content": "<p>We keep this privacy statement under regular review and will place any updates on this website. We will publish any changes we make to this data protection policy on our website.</p>\n<p>This privacy statement was last updated January 2024. </p>"
  },
  {
    "key": "f028f33a-6092-47f4-9eb5-e0df64544408",
    "name": "Contact details and further advice",
    "ncContentTypeAlias": "centralBlocks",
    "title": "Contact details and further advice",
    "content": "<p>If you have any queries about the processing of your personal data as described above, please contact the University’s Data Protection Officer. You can do this by</p>\n<p>Email: <a href=\"mailto:dataprotection@qmu.ac.uk\">dataprotection@qmu.ac.uk</a></p>\n<p>Post:</p>\n<p>Data Protection Officer<br />Queen Margaret University<br />Queen Margaret University Drive <br />Musselburgh <br />EH21 6UU</p>"
  },
  {
    "key": "144d25bf-09ad-414d-af7f-f9890fade293",
    "name": "How to complain",
    "ncContentTypeAlias": "centralBlocks",
    "title": "How to complain",
    "content": "<p>If you have any concerns about our use of your personal information, you can make a complaint to us by contacting the Data Protection Officer in the first instance.</p>\n<p>You can also complain to the ICO if you are unhappy with how we have used your data.</p>\n<p>The ICO’s address:</p>\n<p>Information Commissioner’s Office<br />Wycliffe House<br />Water Lane<br />Wilmslow<br />Cheshire<br />SK9 5AF</p>\n<p>Helpline number: 0303 123 1113</p>\n<p>ICO website: <a href=\"https://www.ico.org.uk\">https://www.ico.org.uk</a></p>"
  }
]]]></Value>
